title: The Unplugged Forum
description:
The Unplugged Forum presents live music every Wednesday night from 7pm - 10pm starting March 6th. Enjoy dinner, drinks and music under the stars on the Prairie Fire rooftop.

3/13/2019 | Deep Blue Dream
3/20/2019 | August Young
3/27/2019 | Los Gatos
4/3/2019 | August Young
4/10/2019 | Crimson Skye
4/24/2019 | Joshua Wade Aginer
